query:
SELECT
                q.queue_id,
                q.name,
                q.priority,
                ARRAY_AGG(qca.cluster_id ORDER BY qca.order) FILTER (WHERE qca.cluster_id IS NOT NULL) as "cluster_targets: Vec<Uuid>"
            FROM
                queues q
            LEFT JOIN
                queue_cluster_assignments qca ON q.queue_id = qca.queue_id
            GROUP BY
                q.queue_id
            ORDER BY
                q.priority ASC;
